80
0:03:27.26,000 --> 0:03:29,000
We don't need a media company

81
0:03:29.26,000 --> 0:03:31,000
to help do this for us.

82
0:03:31.26,000 --> 0:03:34,000
So the traditional media companies, of course,

83
0:03:34.26,000 --> 0:03:37,000
are paying very close attention to these online communities.

84
0:03:37.26,000 --> 0:03:4,000
They know this is the mass audience of the future;

85
0:03:40.26,000 --> 0:03:42,000
they need to figure it out.

86
0:03:42.26,000 --> 0:03:44,000
