113
0:04:44.26,000 --> 0:04:47,000
whether you like "Buffy the Vampire Slayer"

114
0:04:47.26,000 --> 0:04:49,000
rather than how old you are.

115
0:04:49.26,000 --> 0:04:52,000
That would tell me something more substantial about you.

116
0:04:53.26,000 --> 0:04:55,000
Now there's something else that we've discovered about social media

117
0:04:55.26,000 --> 0:04:57,000
that's actually quite surprising.

118
0:04:57.26,000 --> 0:04:59,000
It turns out that women

119
0:04:59.26,000 --> 0:05:02,000
